Linda didn't invent it.

492
01:03:17,513 --> 01:03:19,639
All right, Giuliana, you're right.

493
01:03:19,681 --> 01:03:23,101
Don't say "yes" as if I were...

494
01:03:25,227 --> 01:03:30,106
