497
01:03:49,289 --> 01:03:51,206
Damn!

498
01:04:02,215 --> 01:04:04,176
No doubts,
it's smallpox, cholera or leprosy!

499
01:04:04,217 --> 01:04:06,510
Don't exaggerate!

500
01:04:06,594 --> 01:04:09,388
